{"tid":3880,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"2016DSE完嘅你 依家過成點","createTime":"2016-11-26T10:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T11:22:48.000Z","uid":17891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d103909ea91036a8f3909e5eaf0cecc02d3d2d4b","tid":3880,"uid":17891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f02f177e3946adea7159f6a925f3a9d74ada91","tid":3880,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"經過左一個洗禮咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78fb1104e843e31535c6687f85be295555b424c","tid":3880,"uid":17891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T12:07:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>經過左一個洗禮咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分享下吧 巴打"},{"pid":"46a561fdcde2b9749f4b461f570a906a0b23f041","tid":3880,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:23:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>經過左一個洗禮咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分享下吧 巴打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n考之前就覺得如果考衰左就天塌下來咁 又同自修室友一齊並肩作戰 成個感覺好溫暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但考完講完最後一條英文說話題目 就一個個咁quit whatsapp group 之後再去自修室 覺得好冷清 <br />\n好似一套做左6年既戲係兩個月左右既時間就落左幕咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得返自己一個坐係個熄左燈既舞台 得返spotlight射住我咁 道別未算甚麼...<br />\n考完之後放榜成績唔理想 令自己為前途諗好多野 算係成長左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5a586571d3a1e75c0475b0c02cb9475058da2d","tid":3880,"uid":24639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>經過左一個洗禮咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分享下吧 巴打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n考之前就覺得如果考衰左就天塌下來咁 又同自修室友一齊並肩作戰 成個感覺好溫暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但考完講完最後一條英文說話題目 就一個個咁quit whatsapp group 之後再去自修室 覺得好冷清 <br />\n好似一套做左6年既戲係兩個月左右既時間就落左幕咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得返自己一個坐係個熄左燈既舞台 得返spotlight射住我咁 道別未算甚麼...<br />\n考完之後放榜成績唔理想 令自己為前途諗好多野 算係成長左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n考之前都以為DSE係好大件事<br />\n但而家望反轉頭發覺都無乜大不了"},{"pid":"31044794ef1556e41784357d597a44c17bb99102","tid":3880,"uid":23972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:30:32.000Z","msg":"入左鯨大  過左一個月就quit左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a8f1a71a2b834c8a4685d8e18cd5241650ae11","tid":3880,"uid":14293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"Asso 仔，之前日日夜夜都係自修室都温<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後英文2左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf99daca6979bb2ac8a605478c844d6859b1a75","tid":3880,"uid":10620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T18:21:37.000Z","msg":"Jupas派左屎大就去左第度讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab4aa9c7345fc3dbc96b3472b6880083e0d507e","tid":3880,"uid":4468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T18:24:15.000Z","msg":"適應唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb52ca0db6d1e82941a358df99cc9d099882a74b","tid":3880,"uid":22316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-1